    "body": "Right, returning individual lines as individual pipeline entries instead of multiline strings is expected.\r\n\r\nThe other difficulty is ensuring that overlapping lines are only returned once, the way that `-Context 2` correctly handles:\r\n\r\n```powershell\r\n➜ ~ \"ABCDEFGHIJKL\".ToCharArray() | Select-String \"B|D\" -Context 2\r\n\r\n  A\r\n> B\r\n  C\r\n> D\r\n  E\r\n  F\r\n\r\n➜ ~\r\n```",
